Phrase: There's a defensive line around here too, Karl.

Name: Karl
Phrase: Yes, Emil, it's too dangerous to continue on our way. There's nowhere to run if the enemies spot us.

Name: Emil
Phrase: That's because you're slow, Karl. I'd wish you'd could run a bit faster.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Yoshino, what do you think?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Suspiciousness max. They're talking about defensive lines and enemies.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: They're too young to join the army or gendarmerie. Perhaps they're spies sent by some organisation.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Organisation, like the Resistance?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: I don't know. But we can't just let them lurk around.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Hold it right there, you two. What are you doing here?

Name: Karl
Phrase: WHOA!? Enemy soldiers!

Name: Emil
Phrase: Karl, calm down! It's true that they're wearing military uniforms, but they're not the enemy.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: I'm Yakutsk from the Eisengrad Army, she's Yoshino from the Nishiki Army, and we're patrolling the area in cooperation with the Verforet Gendarmerie.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Oh, ooooh-?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Is that how it is this time?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Don't tell them we're members of the SSS yet. Just go with my flow.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ryoukai.

Name: Karl
Phrase: Hello Yakutsk, I'm Karl, slow but steady, Emil's elder brother.

Name: Emil
Phrase: Hello Yoshino, I'm Emil, stubborn but speedy, Karl's younger brother.

Name: Karl & Emil
Phrase: And together, we are Karl and Emil!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Is Verforet full of silly people like this?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Why are you two hanging around here? Didn't you just say something about defensive lines and enemies?

Name: Karl
Phrase: Yeah, that's cause...

Name: Karl
Phrase: What should I do, Emil? How should I explain in this case?

Name: Emil
Phrase: That's where the brawny ones like you are lousy at. Leave it to me, I'll explain to them.

Name: Karl
Phrase: Yeah, I'll leave it to you.

Name: Emil
Phrase: So let me explain why we are lost in this strange place.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: The way you talk sure doesn't sound like you're a child. As if you're used to negotiating.

Name: Emil
Phrase: Yakutsk, and Yoshino, I assure you we are not suspicious. It's true. We have no intention of misbehaving in this forest.

Name: Emil
Phrase: Actually, we were playing a game here. We were divided into two teams and we were playing capture the flag. This is the enemy team's defensive line. Karl and I wanted to sneak in and take the other team's flag.

Name: Karl
Phrase: But when we got into the forest, everything changed. There were trenches, pillboxes and Mist Monsters. We were walking around trying to get to safety, and we got more and more lost.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Regarding that, Yoshino and friends are still investigating. Don't know anything in detail.

Name: Emil
Phrase: If we can get to the west of the forest, we'll be able to find our papa and mama. But how can we head west while avoiding these trenches and pillboxes?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Wouldn't west be where the gendarmerie's station is located? From here, the safest route is to go around from the northern side of the forest.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: If your otou-san and oka-san are waiting for you, you must go back quickly. Wait, will show you the map now.

Name: Karl
Phrase: That would be great. There are iron fortresses all the way to the south and to the west. We were wondering how to get around them.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Wait a minute? You said there are more fortresses further west from here?

Name: Karl
Phrase: Yes, there are. All the pillboxes in Ouvrage Fermont are intimidat...

Name: Karl
Phrase: Oh...

Name: Emil
Phrase: KARL!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Ya boys know a bit too much about these ruins. How do you know that these ruins are iron fortresses if you're simply lost? I'm quite sure no one else has been in here to investigate yet, you know?

Name: Emil
Phrase: Ugh, that's, I read about it in an old book at...

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Where did you read that book? We have a girl in our group who's been reading every single book about Verforench ruins. Even that kid didn't know anything about these Iron Fortresses.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: And, this Ouvrage Fermont you mentioned, its something that's never heard of before. Isn't this place called Schoenenbourg?

Name: Emil
Phrase: I see, so we're already at the Ouvrage Schoenenbourg...

Name: Karl
Phrase: Emil, snatch the map! We're going to turn around from the north and head west, just like these girls said!

Name: Emil
Phrase: Yeah, now we can break through the defensive line!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ah, Yoshino's map!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: I'm not letting you get away! We're taking you both into custody!

Name: Emil
Phrase: No way. You won't be able to catch us.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Don't ya dare underestimate me! Don't ya dare bunch me together with those ordinary soldiers...

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Impossible!? I'm very sure I grabbed...

Name: Emil
Phrase: Farewell then, Yakutsk and Yoshino, I'm happy that you two are the only ones we've met. Thanks to you, we didn't have to waste time fighting.

Name: Karl
Phrase: Thanks for the map. You girls are very kind. As a small thank you, I'll tell you a way out of here.

Name: Karl
Phrase: The most terrifying part of Ouvrage Schoenenbourg is the Minecart Graveyard, if you get trapped there, look for the steel floorboards. You should be able to get out through the vents to the fortress ammunition store.

Name: Emil
Phrase: Hmhmm... Be careful of the minecarts inside the fortress.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Tch, those twerps weren't human...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Nee Yakutsk, aren't you and Yoshino in trouble by any chance?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Seems like it. Gonna be tough for the two of us alone to break through.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Yoshino, two whistles!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ryoukai! Phantom Mist hassai, requesting reinforcements!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Two whistles!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Reinforcements requested. We all need to go now!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: There's Phantom Mist inside the ruins too! Are these ruins the source of the Phantom Mist after all?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: But there's a very thick Mist in the forest, Yakutsk and Yoshino can't hold it alone.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: We can't eliminate them even if we go. Let's cover their retreat to the tochka!
Yakutsk and Yoshino followed the boys out of the tochka. Although they should have been within visual range, the sound of their whistle sounded a long way away.
